{"tid":1068252,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的 我唔小心傳左性病比其他人","createTime":"2019-03-19T05:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T06:19:52.000Z","uid":220307,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f35635cd182c9fc054db307090a50859681b0882","tid":1068252,"uid":220307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"話說小弟兩日前返大陸，見到有棵梅花樹，小弟見到棵梅花樹有個樹窿，忍唔住除褲對住個樹窿執左劑。返左香港之後發現自己好唔舒服，又發燒又頭痛同埋皮疹。跟住睇完醫生發現自己中左梅毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都知自己衰，所以我上網睇過有咩方法會傳染比人，睇完發現原來握手都會傳播梅毒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁啱學校又搞陸運會，小弟衝動報左接力賽。開跑前老師仲叫我除手套，之後睇住啲同學一個一個咁揸住嗰支我拎過嘅接力棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家小弟好後悔，有冇人可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:~<br />\n<br />\n附上梅毒傳播方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/omk8obm.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2Fomk8obm.html&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=e320b298\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/omk8obm.html</a>"},{"pid":"c19b61b550f567403964720e3c4ddda7261bb18f","tid":1068252,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"很好笑，謝謝"},{"pid":"e8c3b42c3e217ed5d50f961369a0502c0da84344","tid":1068252,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:05:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"362f237ac1b08cf2b93525cb43083c2964a0a9da","tid":1068252,"uid":95637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"你唔好on9啦"},{"pid":"4071daf76a8dc317178af1c5c7562c9fff0d2b99","tid":1068252,"uid":224741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f35635cd182c9fc054db307090a50859681b0882","tid":1068252,"uid":220307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"話說小弟兩日前返大陸，見到有棵梅花樹，小弟見到棵梅花樹有個樹窿，忍唔住除褲對